data.description: Looking for a move-in ready home? Well, look no further than this one! Just a short drive to Fort Drum, this home has everything you need. Seller has completely remodeled the kitchen with new custom cabinets, laminate countertops, appliances, flooring, and an island. The formal dining room features fresh paint, new flooring, and lots of natural light. On the main floor you’ll find a huge full bath with stand up shower and laundry. The living room has great built-in entertainment area, fresh paint, new flooring, and a natural gas fireplace. Upstairs you’ll find another large full bath with stand up shower and vanity. The bedrooms are all oversized with nice closet space including a huge walk-in closet in the master bedroom. Plenty of room in the garage for your vehicle and a fully fenced yard complete the package.
